{"tid":1951844,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"左膠的甲級罪行 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-03-31T08:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T13:33:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d167a0336121cd752ff265c423bf06aae448214","tid":1951844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200331/20890478/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200331%2F20890478%2F&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=03e9be34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200331%2F20890478%2F&h=285c8106\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200331/20890478/</a><br />\n<br />\n左膠的甲級罪行 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200331/large/1585562386_5943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200331%2Flarge%2F1585562386_5943.jpg&h=c4b70e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交通大學「文化研究國際中心」短片截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n最近不少讀者對我說，蘇哲安教授和撐他的學界朋友都是所謂「左膠」，恕我不敢苟同。長期讀者該留意到，我甚少寫「左膠」一詞，不因為我否定左膠的存在，而是「左膠」已被濫用到一個點，淪為意義不明的貶義詞，失去應有的尖銳，做不到見血封喉的效果。<br />\n<br />\n要論斷一個人，我情願按其具體言行，加以具體褒貶，例如蘇哲安教授，我的評語很客觀，也很中立，那就是「涉嫌誹謗的學棍」七字，每個字都有充分的事實根據。稱他為「左膠」，你根本沒有貶損他，只是抬舉他；至於為蘇教授搖旗吶喊的本地「學者」（恕我不指名道姓），亦當作如是觀。拜託，不要再用「左膠」來「美化」他們了。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「左膠」，一般泛指脫離現實、空談大愛包容的左翼分子。有些不熟悉網絡語言的長輩，一直以為指親共左派，實在是天大誤會。以我觀察，左膠在現實世界大約分為三種：一是「類左膠」，即左而不膠，卻被無理冠上「左膠」污名的左翼；二是「真左膠」，即言行一致的左膠；三是「偽左膠」，即滿嘴左翼理論，但其身不正的偽君子。以我所見，第三類可能最多，所以「左膠」往往也是「偽左膠」的簡稱。<br />\n<br />\n現在大義凜然反歧視的蘇哲安，任教於法國尚慕蘭里昂第三大學，我有讀者是他的舊生，告知一些鮮為人知的「趣事」，例如他曾被學生投訴「性別歧視」。有一班全是女生（讀者即其一），某同學表示畢業後前路茫茫，很焦慮，蘇哲安即當眾說：「Hey don't worry about that cuz, anyway, you girls just finish your studies, get married, and make babies!」女生畢業後就要結婚生子？這種「性別定型」的鬼話，真要勞煩蘇教授的朋友何式凝博士來評一下。<br />\n<br />\n左膠的罪不在「左」，而在「膠」，其可惡可恨處，孟子早說得一清二楚：「所惡執一者，為其賊道也，舉一而廢百也。」左膠之錯，不在反對種族歧視，而在濫用「種族歧視」罪名；不是錯在包容弱者，而是錯在縱容敗類。正因為左膠要做「大愛包容反歧視」的代言人，反而令大眾誤解和厭惡「大愛包容反歧視」，這就叫「賊道」。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"97cbded2d2f386608f8bc36515d479470cf1eef4","tid":1951844,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"「Hey don't worry about that cuz, anyway, you girls just finish your studies, get married, and make babies!」<br />\n如果呢句嘢佢係喺美國嘅大學講 咁果間大學唔知又要唔見幾多億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7db529de766091dd6f529882d6bc10b3087b93","tid":1951844,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfd6755c84a825e85ad46744819c6f4b4abbd98","tid":1951844,"uid":271171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"呢條文要廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38086e6e8a8420ca733f87a6c043aa318bf3e104","tid":1951844,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"大大力推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>左膠死全家</strong></span>"}]}